tag name|||Synth Riders: The Midnight - "Jason"
tag jj|||Synth Riders goes “Back to the Synths” to celebrate 5 years of riding the rails with the “Synthwave Essentials Volume 3” music pack!  Headlined by The Midnight, this 10 song pack (5 free songs, 5 paid DLC) also features a brand new cover of New Order’s classic “Blue Monday”, created just for Synth Riders by legendary DJ Zardonic!  Also in the pack are tracks and remixes featuring Starcadian, GoST, Ollie Wride, Dance With The Dead, Scandroid, LeBrock and PRIZM. Enjoy these great tracks in “Back to the Synths”, one of our original play Stages which has received a special “glow-up” to coincide with our birthday!Add “Jason” by The Midnight (feat. Nikki Flores) to your library!Paying stylistic homage to classic 80s tracks like “Maniac” with the perfect drums plus a killer sax, this track from their first full-length album “Endless Summer” features the voice of Nikki Flores to keep you running and dancing.
